OL,3,CSheffield gets biggest emergency rough
OL,4,Csleeping grant outside London
OL,6,FSheffield City Council has received
OL,7,Fthe largest grant of any local
OL,8,Fauthority outside London as part of
OL,9,Femergency funding to deal with
OL,10,Fhomelessness.
OL,12,FThe #241,000 grant is designed to
OL,13,Fsupport people sleeping rough during
OL,14,Fthe winter.
