OL,3,CSheffield gets biggest emergency rough
OL,4,Csleeping grant outside London
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,7,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,8,FGovernment said: "Sheffield is making
OL,9,Fprogress in their efforts to tackle
OL,10,Frough sleeping pressures, with a focus
OL,11,Fon addressing instances of long-term
OL,12,Frough sleeping which is having an
OL,13,Fimpact in the local area.
OL,15,F"This additional funding will support
OL,16,Fthe local authority to maintain a
OL,17,Fstrong focus on supporting individuals
OL,18,Fwith a history of long-term rough
OL,19,Fsleeping into accommodation this
OL,20,Fwinter."
