OL,3,CSheffield gets biggest emergency rough
OL,4,Csleeping grant outside London
OL,6,FThe cash is part of #10million
OL,7,Fallocated to councils across the UK,
OL,8,Fmore than #1m of which has been
OL,9,Fawarded to those in Yorkshire and
OL,10,Fnorthern Lincolnshire.
OL,12,FSixteen areas in total across the
OL,13,Fregion will benefit.
OL,15,FLeeds (#155,000), York (#87,000) and
OL,16,FBradford (#48,000) are among those to
OL,17,Freceive support.
